CatDescriptText: Cutline for image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 14, 1973, p. 25, reads: "Summer Youth Sports Program Set - Fred Lucas... Coordinator of Basketball."  Portion of accompanying article by Ben Wilson reads: "Once again, the University of Pittsburgh will be funded to conduct a National Summer Youth Sports  Program.  And in the past, the project at Pitt will be operated in conjunction with the Leisure-Learn Program.  The National Summer Youth Sports Program (NSYSP) is authorized, by and funded by, the United States Congress... - All Photos by Harris"
TitMainTitle: Fred Lucas, Schenley High School physical education instructor, standing outside of Trees Hall, University of Pittsburgh, Oakland
